# ============================================================================
# v2 engine + editor — gitignore
# ============================================================================

# ---- Build outputs (root) --------------------------------------------------
editor-cpp.exe
editor-cpp.exp
editor-cpp.ilk
editor-cpp.lib
editor-cpp.obj
editor-cpp.pdb
hello.exe
hello.exp
hello.ilk
hello.lib
hello.obj
hello.pdb
vc140.pdb

# ---- Object files (MAKE.bat dumps every translation unit to root) ---------
*.obj
*.o

# ---- Date-stamped cache (native-Sat05232026.obj, backend-...) -------------
native-*.obj
backend-*.obj

# ---- Cook outputs ---------------------------------------------------------
cook.zip
cook*.csv

# ---- Editor auto-generated stubs (per-project, Phase 6a) -------------------
.luarc/
.luarc.json

# ---- User-specific editor state (ImGui dock layout, recent projects, ...) -
.settings.ini

# ---- IDE state ------------------------------------------------------------
.vs/
.vscode/
*.user
*.suo
*.sln.cache
*.opensdf
*.sdf

# ---- OS junk --------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
ehthumbs.db
$RECYCLE.BIN/

# ---- Editor backup files --------------------------------------------------
*.swp
*~
*.bak
*.orig

# ---- Build / runtime logs -------------------------------------------------
*.log

# ---- Engine cook-cache (in-place .X.png hidden-prefix from cook() recipe) -
# Példa: assets/audio/.foo.mp3 (a motor cook-cache rejtett-prefix fájlokat
# generál minden cook(path)-hoz). MAKE.bat tidy egyébként törli.
# A pattern bizonytalan ezért a meglevő egyértelmű kiterjesztéseket fedjük le.
**/.*.png
**/.*.jpg
**/.*.jpeg
**/.*.tga
**/.*.bmp
**/.*.iqm
**/.*.gltf
**/.*.glb
**/.*.fbx
**/.*.obj
**/.*.lua
**/.*.mp3
**/.*.wav
**/.*.ogg
**/.*.flac
**/.*.mod
**/.*.xm
**/.*.s3m
**/.*.it
**/.*.tmx
**/.*.json5
